# Shared agent contract — committed and hand-tailored to this repo (see AGENTS.md).
# Everything under .claude/ is ignored EXCEPT the shared hooks, skills, and settings;
# per-user overrides go in .claude/settings.local.json and stay ignored.
.claude/*
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/settings.json

# Local multi-agent review scratch artifacts (comprehensive-review skill)
.full-review/
